@hypebeastkicks: @willsmith and @spidadmitchell have teamed up for a @belairathletics x @adidas D.O.N. Issue #3 "Prep School" Collection. Each iteration of the Utah Jazz superstar’s signature silhouette is inspired by Mitchell’s journey through prep school and ushers in playful patterns and colors that are inspired by certain outfits that Will Smith rocked in the iconic American sitcom The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air.
